<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="spare-vt">spare <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /speə(r)/    美 /sper/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>抽出；腾出；剩下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>I can’t spare</strong> the <strong>time</strong>.
我抽不出时间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Could you spare one of your staff to help us out?
你能不能从你的手下中抽一个人来帮帮我们？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They still have some <strong>money to spare</strong>.
他们还有一些余钱。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>spare sth / sb for:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We can only spare one room for you.
我们只能给你腾出一个房间。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>spare sb sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He said he could spare me only ten minutes.
他说他只能抽出十分钟的时间给我。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>不伤害；赦免</strong></h4>
<p>to not hurt or damage sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>spare</strong> sb’s <strong>life</strong>
饶某人一命</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>节约；吝惜：</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="spare-no-expense-effort">spare no expense / effort</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不惜工本；全力以赴：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>For the sake of the welfare of our offspring, we should spare no effort to protect our mother planet.
为了造福子孙后代，我们应不遗余力地保护我们的地球母亲。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>They started off late and got to the airport with minutes to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (剩下).  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. spare  </p></div>